First time try their menu no.4, breaded fish with rice. This menu comes with beans and salad. Beans served not cold, which is good. Salad also taste fresh, veggies still crunchy. The breaded fried fish crunchy and meaty inside. What surprising is their brown sauce goes well with the rice n meal. Must try when you around here. My fussy picky eater daughter even said, i like the food.
My son loves their chicken chop with rice. Rated it as one of the best if not the best around here.

Come and try their western! Cheap and super good , especially the sauce they offer in the chicken chop rice. Always my favourite western, this is like the second best Western in my opinion. Uncle is very kind there too!
